name: 贾里德·布雷兹
name_full: 贾里德·布雷兹 Jared Breeze
birth_place: 美国，加利佛利亚州南部
introduction: Jared was born in Southern California where he still lives with his parents and younger brother Devin.Being completely natural in front of the camera, it was no surprise that he found himself on the Jimmy Kimmel show after accidently running into the taping of the show on Halloween. Soon some regional and international commercials followed. Currently he broadens his skills by working on independent and short movies.When not working Jared goes to school, spends time with his family and friends. He enjoys reading, swimming in the local swim team, going to the beach in the summer to snorkel and boogie board and skiing in the mountains during the winter.
